import React from 'react'
import BigDisplay from '../components/BigDisplay'
import Content from '../components/Content'
import TextField from '../components/TextField'
import Button from '../components/Button'
import Error from '../components/Error'

import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row'
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'

export default (props) => {

    return (
    <>
        <BigDisplay
            title="Who mananges your company?"
            subTitle="Please provide the details below either on the individual that is the majority owner of the company or a high-level management official whose main responsibility is the effective operation of the company."
        />
        <Error page="fifthPage" />
        <Content>
            <TextField linked="First_Name" label="First Name" />
            <TextField linked="Last_Name" label="Last Name" />
            <TextField linked="Date_Birth" label="Date of Birth" />
            <TextField linked="Residential_Address" label="Residential Address" />
            <TextField linked="Manager_Postal_Code" label="Postal Code" />
            <TextField linked="Manager_City" label="City" />
            <TextField linked="Manager_Country" label="Country" />

            <Row className="menuRow">
                <Col md={2} lg={2} sm={1} xs={1}></Col>
                <Col md={6} lg={6} sm={10} xs={10}>
                    <Button className="white" onClick={props.btnPrev}>Back</Button>
                    <Button onClick={props.btnNext}>Next</Button>
                </Col>
                <Col md={4} lg={4} sm={1} xs={1}></Col>
            </Row>
      </Content>
    </>)
}
